
i2c addresses

0x10 - PA1010D - GPS
0x18 - MCP9808 - temperature 
0x39 - APDS-9960 - colour 
0x40 - INA219 - leisure battery voltage
0x41 - INA219 - solar battery voltage
0x44 - INA219 - car battery voltage
0x68 - DS1307 - Real-Time Clock 

pins 

A0 - 
D1 - SCL 
D2 - SDA 
D3 - 
D4 - SD Card chip select
D5 - SPI SCK
D6 - SPI MISO
D7 - SPI MOSI
D8 - EPD cip select

